text: Eldar Salihović (; born 17 June 1999) is a Montenegrin alpine skier. He competed in giant slalom at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Montenegrin male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Montenegro Category:Alpine skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
